uritools
========================================================================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/uritools
    :target: https://pypi.org/project/uritools
    :alt: Latest PyPI version

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/github/actions/workflow/status/tkem/uritools/ci.yml
